        public boolean toBoolean()
        Description copied from interface: IChangeValue
        Converts this value to a boolean.
        Specified by:
        toBoolean in interface IChangeValue
        Returns:
        a boolean representation of this value. if IChangeValue.isSnowflake() returns true then this method will return true.
        if the type of this value is a String this method will check if the IChangeValue.toString() representation has more than 0 characters
        all other types are checked as a falsy value. ei, if this value's type is a number type then we check if the value is not equal to 0.
